OL,3,CHealth Secretary to strip disgraced
OL,4,Csurgeon Ian Paterson of his #1m pension
OL,6,FThe Health Secretary is to strip
OL,7,Fdisgraced breast surgeon Ian Paterson
OL,8,Fof his #1 million pension pot.
OL,10,FPaterson is currently serving a 20-
OL,11,Fyear prison sentence after being found
OL,12,Fto have carried out unnecessary and
OL,13,Funapproved procedures on more than
OL,14,F1,000 breast cancer patients over a
OL,15,Fperiod of some 14 years.
OL,17,FInquests into the deaths of 62
OL,18,Fpatients who were treated by Paterson
OL,19,Fare to open this month, with another
OL,20,F20 opening later.
