OL,3,CHealth Secretary to strip disgraced
OL,4,Csurgeon Ian Paterson of his #1m pension
OL,6,FAccording to The Sunday Times, Wes
OL,7,FStreeting has decided to remove
OL,8,FPaterson's taxpayer-funded pension
OL,9,Funder rules that allow NHS benefits to
OL,10,Fbe forfeited in the case of criminal,
OL,11,Fnegligent or fraudulent acts.
OL,13,FThe newspaper reported that the
OL,14,FSecretary of State must authorise the
OL,15,Fdecision and, to qualify, the offences
OL,16,Fmust be considered so serious as to
OL,17,Flead to a "serious loss of confidence
OL,18,Fin the public service" or to have been
OL,19,F"gravely injurious to the state".
