OL,3,CHealth Secretary to strip disgraced
OL,4,Csurgeon Ian Paterson of his #1m pension
OL,6,FPaterson, 64, was employed by the
OL,7,FHeart of England NHS Foundation Trust
OL,8,Fand practised in the independent
OL,9,Fsector at Spire Parkway and Spire
OL,10,FLittle Aston in Birmingham.
OL,12,FHe was jailed in 2017 after being
OL,13,Fconvicted of 17 counts of wounding
OL,14,Fwith intent and three counts of
OL,15,Funlawful wounding relating to
OL,16,Funnecessary operations performed on 10
OL,17,Fpatients between 1997 and 2011.
