OL,3,CHealth Secretary to strip disgraced
OL,4,Csurgeon Ian Paterson of his #1m pension
OL,6,FAn independent inquiry, chaired by
OL,7,Fformer Bishop of Norwich, the Right
OL,8,FRev Graham James, ruled in February
OL,9,F2020 that Paterson had carried out
OL,10,Fhundreds of unnecessary operations on
OL,11,Fscores of patients, exaggerating or
OL,12,Finventing cancer risks.
OL,14,FA spokesman for the Department of
OL,15,FHealth and Social Care said: "These
OL,16,Fwere appalling crimes and we are
OL,17,Fassisting His Majesty's Coroner with
OL,18,Fthe inquests concerning the tragic
OL,19,Fdeaths of patients previously treated
OL,20,Fby Ian Paterson. We offer our sincere
OL,21,Fcondolences to the families.
