OL,3,CHealth Secretary to strip disgraced
OL,4,Csurgeon Ian Paterson of his #1m pension
OL,6,F"Cases like this are fortunately rare,
OL,7,Fbut this Government will prioritise
OL,8,Fpatient safety to ensure everyone
OL,9,Freceives the high-quality, safe
OL,10,Ftreatment they deserve.
OL,12,F"We understand families' frustration
OL,13,Fand recognise that significant
OL,14,Fimprovements to patient safety are
OL,15,Frequired.
OL,17,F"This Government is working urgently
OL,18,Fto ensure all lessons from this
OL,19,Fterrible case are being learned."
